 is not his testicle.\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 3117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It seems his tight is torn around that area.\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Social media is fast becoming a fake news hub.\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"#Paris2024 #paris2024olympics #Paris.\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3241, \"end\": 3246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.158707733870589e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"LATEST DEVELOPMENTS:Giovanni Pernice crisis deepens as Laura Whitmore makes statement on BBC Strictly sagaLady Gaga Olympics gig slammed as fans rage at 'woke' performance and dancer slip-upBBC Olympics viewers fume 'waste of license fee money' as Tom Hiddleston cameo baffles fans'Come Los Angeles in 2028, I think they will resort to just having it in a stadium.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3303, \"end\": 3317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Whitmore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Whitmore\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Whitmore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Whitmore\"}, {\"begin\": 3337, \"end\": 3340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.622035099472531, \"rank\": 0.6075234016642951, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 3359, \"end\": 3363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.1873150328223236e-28, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"ht