, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GB_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GB News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GB_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GB_News\"}, {\"begin\": 7442, \"end\": 7448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.6698611241748265, \"rank\": 0.49087337788696905, \"text\": \"Sophie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 7449, \"end\": 7455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Overwatch\", \"score\": 0.9906009182119898, \"rank\": 0.009474438519404264, \"text\": \"Reaper\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Overwatch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Overwatch\"}, {\"begin\": 7520, \"end\": 7525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.158707733870589e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even GB News' Anne Diamond ripped apart Friday's display, telling the People's Channel's viewers on Saturday morning: \\\"The ceremony was an abomination, mocking Jesus.\", \"from\": 7775, \"to\": 7941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7789, \"end\": 7801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Diamond\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Diamond\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Diamond\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Diamond\"}, {\"begin\": 7935, \"end\": 7940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999996331803904, \"rank\": 3.668187769806881e-07, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They really do not know how to read a room.\", \"from\": 7942, \"to\": 7985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was disgusting.\\\"\", \"from\": 7986, \"to\": 8005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Showbiz journalist Stephanie Takyi agreed: \\\"To be honest, I do not think they would have done that about Islam because they know that they would have gone to the streets and it would have been a wrap for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 8007, \"to\": 8224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8026, \"end\": 8035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_McMahon\", \"score\": 0.9854580871874736, \"rank\": 0.014644204421714055, \"text\": \"Stephanie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_McMahon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_McMahon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They feel like for Christianity, because we are quite subdued, let us make a mockery of it.\", \"from\": 8226, \"to\": 8318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8246, \"end\": 8258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9978612607155566, \"rank\": 0.002143315830872905, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just think some things are sacred, and maybe that could have just been left out of the show.\\\"\", \"from\": 8319, \"to\": 8414, \"entities\": []}]}"